<span id="freeTextContainer14008730574445761063"><br/> <br/> Disappointing. The plot had so much potential and I love anything paranormal, but throughout the whole book I felt like I was waiting for the story to actually begin. There was absolutely NO chemistry between the two leads. Nada. </span>

