<div id="review_98195616" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/98195616" />
    <a title="Suzanne (Under the Covers Book blog)" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3575839-suzanne-under-the-covers-book-blog"><img alt="Suzanne (Under the Covers Book blog)" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1583236251p2/3575839.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/98195616?book_show_action=true">Apr 12, 2010</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Suzanne (Under the Covers Book blog)" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Suzanne (Under the Covers Book blog)" href="/user/show/3575839-suzanne-under-the-covers-book-blog">Suzanne (Under the Covers Book blog)</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3575839-suzanne-under-the-covers-book-blog?shelf=demons">demons</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3575839-suzanne-under-the-covers-book-blog?shelf=genre-paranormal-romance">genre-paranormal-romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3575839-suzanne-under-the-covers-book-blog?shelf=va-va-voom-vampires">va-va-voom-vampires</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3575839-suzanne-under-the-covers-book-blog?shelf=heroine-annoys-the-shit-out-of-me">heroine-annoys-the-shit-out-of-me</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3575839-suzanne-under-the-covers-book-blog?shelf=author-jeaniene-frost">author-jeaniene-frost</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer98195616" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13358895074387112381"><b>3.5 Stars</b><br/><br/>This didn&apos;t have the hot chemistry that the Night Huntress series has, and for me Spade fell flat a bit as a romantic lead and I found Denise a bit annoying. <i>But</i> I still enjoyed it, I think if this were written by anyone else other than Jeaniene Frost, and I hadn&apos;t already read the Night Huntress series I probably would have rated it higher; however, I have and I guess I expected a bit more.</span>
  <span id="freeText13358895074387112381" style="display:none"><b>3.5 Stars</b><br /><br />This didn't have the hot chemistry that the Night Huntress series has, and for me Spade fell flat a bit as a romantic lead and I found Denise a bit annoying. <i>But</i> I still enjoyed it, I think if this were written by anyone else other than Jeaniene Frost, and I hadn't already read the Night Huntress series I probably would have rated it higher; however, I have and I guess I expected a bit more.</span>
